-- ON THE MOVE-RBC Wealth hires financial adviser from Wells Fargo
-- By Avik Das in Bangalore
-- Mon Feb 03, 2014 10:16AM EST
-- None



Feb 3 (Reuters) - RBC Wealth Management said it hired financial adviser James Leslie from Wells Fargo Advisors.

Leslie, an industry veteran with 32 years of experience, managed about $140 million in assets at Wells Fargo. He joined RBC Wealth Management's Pittsburgh office.